{"tid":1464880,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"核爆都唔割","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:34:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:34:27.000Z","uid":84514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0c4d785ced097a061720b7066cd7a48c0ba0b61d","tid":1464880,"uid":84514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:34:17.000Z","msg":"我講緊割包皮打麻醉針果陣，訓著左發夢見到互相鬧，叫人走，叫人留，唔信前線幫手割包皮嘅醫生自己嘅決定，坐係屋企指揮人地點割包皮<br />\n<br />\n最後，醫生嬲嬲豬割左，包皮爛晒，最開心就係外面d狗，因為佢照有肉食，唔會比醫生錫春袋<br />\n<br />\n唔割，核爆都唔割，自己判斷現場應該做咩<br />\n<br />\n唔洗再講其他<br />\n<br />\n明就明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"413626f56eac56eae666a03faeaf47d45cf23156","tid":1464880,"uid":298077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:34:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化不割蓆</span></strong></span>"}]}